        <section name="What is Chenille Kit?">

            <p>
                Chenille Kit is a collection of modules with sophisticated components, services and utils based on
                Tapestry's IOC
                but
                <strong>not</strong>
                only for Tapestry Framework based servlet applications.
            </p>

            <subsection name="The Modules">

                <p>
                    At the moment there exists some modules like:
                </p>

                <ul>
                    <li>Core - core utils we need for some of the following modules</li>
                    <li>Access - [not ready yet]</li>
                    <li>Google - Google based services like Map, Distance, etc</li>
                    <li>Hibernate -</li>
                    <li>Hivemind - a bridge from/to
                        <a href="http://hivemind.apache.org/">HiveMind</a>
                        to
                        <a href="http://tapestry.apache.org/tapestry5/">Tapestry5</a>
                    </li>
                    <li>Image -</li>
                    <li>LDAP -</li>
                    <li>Lucene - indexer and sercher service based on
                        <a href="http://lucene.apache.org/java/docs/index.html">Apache Lucene's</a>
                        fulltext engine.
                    </li>
                    <li>Mail - simple mail service based on
                        <a href="http://commons.apache.org/email/">Apache Commons Email</a>
                    </li>
                    <li>Quartz -
                        <a href="http://www.opensymphony.com/quartz/">Quartz</a>
                        based scheduler services
                    </li>
                    <li>Reports -
                        <a href="http://jasperforge.org/plugins/project/project_home.php?group_id=102">Jasperreports</a>
                        based
                        reporting services
                    </li>
                    <li>Scripting -</li>
                    <li>Tapestry - collection of components and services for your
                        <a href="http://tapestry.apache.org/tapestry5/">Tapestry5</a>
                        Framework based applications
                    </li>
                    <li>Template -
                        <a href="http://velocity.apache.org/">Velocity</a>
                        and
                        <a href="http://freemarker.org/">FreeMarker</a>
                        based
                        template services
                    </li>
                </ul>

            </subsection>

        </section>

